riodic boundary condition\nshould be used. Key words: effective thermal conductivities, anisotropic,\nmulti-relaxation-time, lattice Boltzmann method, three-dimensional\nfour-directional braided composites\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Mar 2015 15:46:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-31"}
